title.Value: ePIC IMPACT: HOW TO SHOOT A BOW AND ARROW: ePISODe 16

description.Name: description
description.Value: This video is about the proper technique of firing a bow and arrow. This technique works for all those whether it be a compound, recurve, or a longbow. My next video will be about the terminology of the sports and the video after that will be a demo and a review of my bow and arrow. The bow I am using today is a PSE Polaris Express with a TruGlo red dot sight and an Octane Hostage Pro arrow rest. Stay tuned for more archery videos!
